data.text: Suman was the rising star of the Telugu industry. His movies ran 100, 200, 300 days. He was tall, knew how to dance, fought like a warrior. Then one day he is arrested. On a complaint by three girls that he took not-so-good pics of them. The end. His career went phat. All the allegations were proved wrong in court but the blue eyed boy lost his sheen and never rose again. Frankly, his life should be made into a movie.
